{
  "texts": [
    "This modification successfully constrained the output, making it more reliable and compatible with the simulation.",
    "However, while some flocking behavior emerged, it was inconsistent.",
    "Small clusters formed briefly, but overall alignment and coherence were weaker than expected.",
    "We compared the resulting headings with those produced by a rule-based model.",
    "While some calculated headings were numerically similar, they often pointed in opposite directions."
  ]
}